# Testing Rules
- Use Vitest for unit tests, Playwright for E2E
- Test file lives next to the source file: `Button.tsx` → `Button.test.tsx`
- Name tests descriptively: `it('renders error state when API fails')`
- Mock external dependencies — never make real network calls in unit tests
- Aim for behavior testing, not implementation testing